Titolo: The Legend of Heroes III: Song of the Ocean

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: The Legend of Heroes III: Song of the Ocean, known in Japan as The Legend of Heroes V: Umi no Oriuta, is a role-playing video game developed by Nihon Falcom. It is the fifth game in The Legend of Heroes series, and the third and final title in the "Gagharv Trilogy". It was originally released for Microsoft Windows in 1999 and was remade for PlayStation Portable in 2006.